{
  "id": "adv_card_hrk_11_01",
  "title": "佐伯遙子 1話 そんな光景を見てみたい",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ十月かぁ……\n時が経つのは早いわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's almost October‚ huh…\nTime really flies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5000,
          "startTime": 5.8
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "おはようございます、遙子さん\nぼーっとカレンダーを見て、どうかしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ Haruko-san.\nYou were staring blankly at the calendar—something on your mind?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "おはよう、{user}君\n実は、麻奈ちゃんのことを思い出していたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good morning‚ {user}-kun.\nActually‚ I was thinking about Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "もうすぐ、麻奈ちゃんのお誕生日でしょう？\n今年はどうお祝いしようかなって考えていたのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Her birthday is coming up soon‚ right?\nI was wondering how to celebrate it this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。確かにそろそろですよね\n今年もちゃんとお祝いしないとだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Yeah‚ it's about that time.\nWe should make sure to celebrate properly this year too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "みんなに声を掛けて、盛大に……なんてどうかしら？\n麻奈ちゃんも、そっちの方が嬉しいでしょうし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What if we invite everyone and make it grand…?\nMana-chan would probably be happier that way.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね。そういえば、麻奈の誕生日に偶然\n月ストのライブがあるんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sounds good. Come to think of it‚ by coincidence‚\nthere's a Moon Tempest live show on Mana's birthday.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃にそのことを伝えたら、「お姉ちゃんをお祝いして\nあげたい」って、追加で一曲、歌うことになりました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I told Kotono‚ she said‚ “I want to celebrate my sister‚”\nso she'll be singing an extra song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃんから麻奈ちゃんへのプレゼント\nっていうことかしら。素敵な歌になりそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So it'll be Kotono-chan's present to Mana-chan‚ right?\nIt sounds like it'll be a lovely song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "大好きな琴乃ちゃんや、会場の人達にお祝いして\nもらえたら、麻奈ちゃんもきっと喜ぶと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being celebrated by her beloved Kotono-chan and the audience—\nMana-chan would surely be delighted.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1599372569,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ。それこそ、盛大なお祝いになりそうです\nあの時、遙子さんが麻奈にしてくれたみたいに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. That would really be a grand celebration.\nJust like what you did for Mana back then‚ Haruko-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "それを言うなら、三枝さんと{user}君と\n私で、だけどね。ふふ、あの時は楽しかったわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If you put it that way‚ it was with Saegusa-san‚ {user}-kun‚\nand me. Fufu‚ that was fun‚ wasn't it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――2017年",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—2017",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.0246955872,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s2",
      "startTime": 90.3666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "え？　麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブがあるの？\nそっか、今年は開催出来るのね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? There's going to be Mana-chan's birthday live?\nI see‚ so it's actually happening this year.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "はい。まだ本人には伝えていないんですが\n大きめの会場で盛大に開催する予定です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. We haven't told her yet‚ though.\nWe plan to hold it in a fairly large venue‚ on a grand scale.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃん、ずっとバースデーライブをやりたかった\nみたいだし、きっと喜ぶと思うわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mana-chan has always wanted to have a birthday live‚\nso I'm sure she'll be happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "だから{user}君もバタバタしてたのね\n昨日も遅くまで打ち合わせしていたみたいだし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's why you've been so busy‚ {user}-kun.\nYou were in meetings until late last night too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "関係各所への連絡や\n他にもいろいろと決めなきゃいけないことが多くて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've had to contact all the parties involved‚\nand there are so many other decisions to make.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今日もこれから、スポンサーへの挨拶回りとか\n会場の下見に行かないといけなくて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Today too‚ I have to go greet the sponsors‚\nand do a site inspection of the venue.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "三枝さんと二人だけじゃ大変そうね……\n私に何か手伝えることはない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That sounds tough with just you and Saegusa-san…\nIs there anything I can help with?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "いやいや、アイドルに手伝わせる訳にはいきませんって\nこういうのは、裏方の仕事ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ no‚ I can't ask an idol to help.\nThis kind of thing is backstage work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.7560432015,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "でも、麻奈ちゃんのバースデーライブなんでしょ？\n事務所の仲間としても、友達としても、見過ごせないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's Mana-chan's birthday live‚ isn't it?\nAs her colleague and her friend‚ I can't just ignore it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "それに人手が増えれば、より大きなことも出来そうだし\n麻奈ちゃんに、もっと喜んでもらえそうじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With more people‚ we could do something bigger‚\nand Mana-chan might be even happier‚ don't you think?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.1999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "だから、お願い\n私に手伝えることがあるなら、手伝わせてほしいの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So please‚\nif there's anything I can do‚ let me help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.2999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました。実は猫の手も借りたかったので\nその申し出はとても助かります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Alright. Honestly‚ I could use all the help I can get.\nYour offer is a huge help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 177.0333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、じゃあ決まりね\n三人で麻奈ちゃんのために、頑張りましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ then it's settled.\nLet's do our best for Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.4333231608,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6300.000000000011,
          "startTime": 189.7333231608
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6499964396
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 187.6499964396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それで、これがバースデーライブ当日の\n予定なんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ this is the schedule for the day\nof the birthday live—…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 191.7333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 193.3333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど～。一番の盛り上げどころは、ライブ終盤……\n新曲の前にある、麻奈ちゃんへのサプライズ……ね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see~. The biggest highlight will be toward the end of the live…\nㅊ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 200.2333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、そこでホールケーキを運んで来る予定ですが……\nええと……ちょっと、地味でしょうか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. That's when we plan to bring in a whole cake…\nUm… Maybe that's a little plain?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.1872715269,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 213.8666631062
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、いいとは思うんだけど……\nケーキって、去年のライブでも贈ってたな～って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm‚ I think it's fine‚ but…\nDidn't we also give her a cake at last year's live…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 218.3333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですね。バースデーライブではなかったですが\n麻奈の誕生日の日にあったライブで贈りましたね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-right. It wasn't a birthday live‚ but there was a concert\non her birthday‚ and we gave her a cake then…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 227.3333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 230.7999964396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ケーキは定番だから外せないわよね\n麻奈ちゃんの好きな味にするのは当然として……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But cake is a classic‚ so we can't leave it out.\nOf course‚ it should be a flavor Mana-chan likes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 235.7333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 239.8333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "あ！　せっかく会場も大きいんだし、ケーキもすっごく\n大きいのを用意しない？　麻奈ちゃんが驚くくらいの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh! Since the venue is big‚ why not prepare\na huge cake‚ big enough to surprise Mana-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 244.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 249.3333297729
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど。シンプルですが、インパクトがありますね\nいいと思います。ただ、準備が間に合うかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Simple‚ but impactful.\nI like it. I just wonder if we can prepare it in time…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 253.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 258.6000025431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "三人で分担すれば大丈夫よ\nケーキの方は、三枝さんと相談して進めておくわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If the three of us divide the tasks‚ we'll be fine.\nI'll discuss the cake with Saegusa-san and handle that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 262.0999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "あとは……バースデーライブなんだから\nファンのみんなも麻奈ちゃんをお祝いしたいわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And then… since it's a birthday live‚\nthe fans will want to celebrate Mana-chan too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 270.4666564941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 273.8666692097
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh015.m4a",
      "text": "ケーキの登場の後、声を合わせて「おめでとう」って\n伝える……とか？　少し普通過ぎる気もしますが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the cake appears‚ everyone could say “Happy Birthday” together—\nor something like that? It might feel a bit too ordinary…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 278.0999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 283.8000025431
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk022.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、素敵だと思う。ステージの上で……\n光の海の中で、大切な人達に伝えてもらえたら、きっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ I think it's wonderful. On the stage…\nIf she hears it from her loved ones amid a sea of lights‚ I'm sure—",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 289.4999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh016.m4a",
      "text": "ステージから見る光景は特別だって\nあいつも、いつも言ってますよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She always says the view\nfrom the stage is special.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 299.0999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 301.3000086466
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk023.m4a",
      "text": "……待って、これってうまく使えないかしら？\n光を使って、麻奈ちゃんにメッセージを伝えるの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Wait‚ couldn't we make use of that?\nWe can use the lights to send a message to Mana-chan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 305.8999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh017.m4a",
      "text": "特定の席の人だけ、ペンライトを点ける……とか？\nさすがに文字を作るのは難しそうですが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like having only certain seats light up their penlights…?\nForming words might be difficult‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 314.9666564941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk024.m4a",
      "text": "文字じゃなくても、いいと思う\n大事なのは、想いを伝えることだもの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It doesn't have to be words.\nWhat matters is conveying the feeling.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 320.9333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 323.8666651407
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk025.m4a",
      "text": "一つ一つの光を、想いを繋げれば、きっと届くわ\nいつか私も、そんな光景を見てみたいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If each light connects with that feeling‚ it'll surely reach her.\nSomeday‚ I want to see such a sight myself…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 331.5333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh018.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haruko-san…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 336.3666651407,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshireception-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hoshireception-00-noon",
      "startTime": 337.8333318073
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk026.m4a",
      "text": "……ううん、なんでもないわ\n実現するのは大変そうだから、一杯頑張らないとね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…No‚ it's nothing.\nMaking it real will be tough‚ so we'll need to work hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 341.2333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "—Live Show Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 346.4866651216,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 347.8333231608
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 347.8333231608
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk027.m4a",
      "text": "なんとか準備は間に合ったわね\nあとは、うまくマークが作れればいいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We somehow finished preparations in time.\nNow I just hope the mark turns out well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 352.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh019.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ。お客さんにも丁寧に説明してくれたじゃ\nないですか。麻奈への光のハートマーク、届くはずです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't worry. You explained it carefully to the audience.\nThe glowing heart for Mana should reach her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 359.9999755859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 365.0333175658
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk028.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。私もそろそろ、席に行こうかしら\nうろうろしてて、サプライズがバレちゃっても大変だし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're right. I should head to my seat soon too.\nIf I keep wandering around‚ I might spoil the surprise.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 370.3999755859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 374.7333460489
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh020.m4a",
      "text": "あ、その前に……あのこと、本当に良かったんですか？\n麻奈の要望でもあったんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ before that… Are you really okay with that decision?\nIt was also Mana's request‚ but still…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 379.5666422526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 381.9666793822
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-hrk029.m4a",
      "text": "バースデーライブへの、ゲスト出演のこと……よね\nうん。今日は仲間として、友達としてお祝いしたいから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You mean about guest performing at the birthday live… right?\nYes. Today I want to celebrate as a colleague and as a friend.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 388.7333089192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_11_01-koh021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、遙子さんはアイドルです\nアイドルとして、麻奈をお祝いしても……",
      "translations": {
